{115}{}{两周前，一个家伙来找我，主动提出要我提供一些信息。他想知道谁最近去世了。。。他们的名字。我不知道他们会挖出尸体。。。[叹气]。。。太可怕了，我需要那笔钱。。。 -- Two weeks ago a guy came to me and offered money for some information. He wanted to know who died recently... their names. I didn't know they were going to dig up and take the bodies... [Sighs]... It's terrible, and I needed that money...}
### {116}{}{Alright, calm down... I'm here to help. Why do these people want to kill you?}
{116}{}{好吧，冷静点。。。我是来帮忙的。为什么这些人要杀了你？ -- Alright, calm down... I'm here to help. Why do these people want to kill you?}
