{117}{}{也许有人看到我们在说话，就向唐森报告。。。和往常一样，他喜欢四处嗅。。。所以这些人变得偏执，决定放弃证据。。。好吧，你知道故事的其余部分。 -- Maybe somebody saw us talking and reported to Donson... As usual, he likes to sniff around... So these guys became paranoid and decided to get rid of the evidence... Well, you know the rest of the story.}
### {118}{}{Where can I find them?}
{118}{}{我在哪里可以找到它们？ -- Where can I find them?}
