{119}{}{我知道他们计划很快做点什么。我打赌他们今晚会在午夜左右出现在墓地。。。 -- I know they planned to do something soon. I bet they are going to show up tonight on the cemetery, around midnight...}
### {120}{}{OK, you stay here now. I'll come back after I've cleared things up.}
{120}{}{好的，你现在留在这里。我把事情弄清楚后再回来。 -- OK, you stay here now. I'll come back after I've cleared things up.}
