{122}{}{哈哈，你做到了！我要离开这个可怕的垃圾场，在一个唐森的猎犬够不到我的地方。再次感谢！ -- Haha, you did it! I'm getting off this awful dump, someplace far away where Donson's hounds can't reach me. Thanks again!}
